// ApprovalButtons
// A row of action buttons with primary, destructive, and default styling.
// Each button briefly shows a loading state for 300ms after being clicked.

FUNCTION handleAction(actionId)
  Sets the loading button to the clicked actionId.
  Calls the onAction callback with the actionId.
  After 300ms, clears the loading state.

---

FUNCTION ApprovalButtons(props) -> ReactNode                              EXPORT
  Renders one button per action in the actions array.
  Button variant (primary/destructive/default) controls color styling.
  The most recently clicked button shows a loading/spinner state for 300ms.
